description: Toyota Innova Crysta is a 7 seater MUV available in a price range of ₹ 17.18 - 24.99 Lakh. In the BS6 era, the Innova Crysta is powered by 2694 cc Petrol engine which produces 164bhp of power and 245Nm of torque.You can have it with a 5-speed Manual or a 6-speed Automatic (Torque Converter) gearbox.
